{"tid":292052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Ive有個痴線幼兒教育導師(發洩文)","createTime":"2017-06-21T04:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T16:51:27.000Z","uid":70552,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de3963688bf9324090d61b160d882250169a1f07","tid":292052,"uid":70552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"叫人帶曬全年既教具返學，最後一件都唔睇，啲教具重到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教案提議比佢既活動ban曬，轉個頭幼稚園老師提議返同一個活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上堂就係到講人是非，連小朋友屋企都攞出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交功課比佢改都唔改就叫人交份修訂版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時交功課睇都唔睇就叫人重做<br />\n有個同學屋企人過左身想請假，佢話唔係父母就唔可以有感情，唔比請假，問號？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幼稚園班主任想探究既活動，返到去佢話完全無意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係幼稚園借既書佢話唔係幼兒書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有主任過黎睇堂就刷曬鞋扮認真教書，面皮成呎厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你威曬啦張老師，連幼稚園老師都話你係痴線既，你都算巴閉。你對教書無熱誠都算，仲要成日玩班學生，如果唔係我地忍你，你收左皮啦，唔該你帶返個腦返學先ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772e05319e3a5d5e0fb50e8724a1c43d7b02d801","tid":292052,"uid":63396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"一齊投訴佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96b8e981795f291f4aa31ae9d7fac4ee07dbb67","tid":292052,"uid":70552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊投訴佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係無途徑去投訴，況且上級點會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c73c8c9a013f0a83e9e415c1505332eab056f46","tid":292052,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c